      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void CachedApiRequest.RequestCache.put(CachedApiRequest<?> request)
      puts a request in the request cache by its url, id, cachePath, and generic runtime type the id is a URL, base 64 encoded SHA-128 hash of the url CachedApiRequest.RequestCache.hashToBase64(String) the path is the relative directory path and the filename getRelativeCachePath() the filename is the id with the file extension getFileExtension() the Type is from getResponseClass() or getResponseType()
